Even old men want toys! While I have a Harley Fat Boy and can in fact ride it, I have always wished that I could move the shifter to the right side or go clutch less. 

Recently I was turned on to a dirt bike solution! An electric bike with amazing dirt bike suspension and enough torque in sport mode to actually ride wheelies 😳. This bike I put together in less than an hour.  It was so much fun that I just continued riding after my leg fell off! No worries, half an hour later I went back to retrieve it!😉👍🏻🇺🇸 Life is as good as you make it…. I’m not done livin!😁🥃🇺🇸. Blessed!!!
